text: The 1927 Kentucky Wildcats football team represented the Kentucky Wildcats of the University of Kentucky during the 1927 college football season.https://www.sports- reference.com/cfb/schools/kentucky/1927-schedule.html The team was led by first-year head coach Harry Gamage. ==Schedule== ==References== Kentucky Category:Kentucky Wildcats football seasons
